e  (  1274–1329 ), who freed Scotland from English domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert Rugge was born in 1387, in England, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with Robert Rugge."},"et":{"1387–Deceased":"1387–Surnud","1385–1420":"1385–1420","1415–1449":"1415–1449","1387–Female":"1387–Surnud","1415":"1415","1387":"1387","1420":"1420","1385":"1385","1449":"1449","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1387–Deceased":"1387–Kuollut","1385–1420":"1385–1420","1415–1449":"1415–1449","1387–Female":"1387–Kuollut","1415":"1415","1387":"1387","1420":"1420","1385":"1385","1449":"1449","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1387–Deceased":"1387–Décédée","1385–1420":"1385–1420","1415–1449":"1415–1449","1387–Female":"1387–Décédée","1415":"1415","1387":"1387","1420":"1420","1385":"1385","1449":"1449","England, United Kingdom":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert Rugge est née en 1387, à Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Robert Rugge."},"de":{"1387–Deceased":"1387–Verstorben","1385–1420":"1385–1420","1415–1449":"1415–1449","1387–Female":"1387–Verstorben","1415":"1415","1387":"1387","1420":"1420","1385":"1385","1449":"1449","England, United Kingdom":"England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Mrs Robert Rugge wurde 1387 in England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mit Robert Rugge mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"1387–Deceased":"1387–Desede","1385–1420":"1385–1420","1415–1449":"1415–1449","1387–Female":"1387–Desede","1415":"1415","1387":"1387","1420":"1420","1385":"1385","1449":"1449","England, United Kingdom":"Angletè, United Kingdom"},"hu":{"1387–Deceased":"1387–elhunyt","1385–1420":"1385–1420","1415–1449":"1415–1449","1387–Female":"1387–elhunyt","1415":"1415","1387":"1387","1420":"1420","1385":"1385","